1 Emergency preamble. Whereas, acts and resolves of the Legislature do not
2 become effective until 90 days after adjournment unless enacted as emergencies; and
3 Whereas, the windfall elimination provision and the government pension offset of the
4 federal Social Security Act reduce social security benefits for certain public employees in
